{"tid":2023990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【屎家軍】幾幅截圖簡單講解點解屎家軍既PO絕對有資格放上時事台","createTime":"2020-05-19T10:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T03:17:30.000Z","uid":88743,"like":122,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"413750c5e428af4e0688fd3fe30eff3c9c69177f","tid":2023990,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"片段link放係PO最底<br />\n<br />\n8:30<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWCzEJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWCzEJ8.jpg&h=8cbeca59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n封殺二字<br />\n覺唔覺得似曾相識?<br />\n<br />\n9:27<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ekMD6o8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FekMD6o8.jpg&h=ccb818d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qz9BS39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQz9BS39.jpg&h=b7a8a120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n17:17<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FyrdaQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFyrdaQQ.jpg&h=3b584d01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慕容呢條片絕對係有質素既片<br />\n封殺二字<br />\n覺唔覺得似曾相識?<br />\n香港藝人被封殺 報章被封殺 <br />\n要異口同聲一種聲音先可以生存<br />\n你覺得咁樣對香港係咪好事?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3O3yke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3O3yke.jpg&h=f0c41c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sm1D6Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsm1D6Fe.jpg&h=331cae4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能你會諗 屌唔好講到呢班友咁高<br />\n要黃既youtuber有大把 有燒山 有細良 有沈旭暉 有杜汶澤 洗撚睇呢班濕鳩咩<br />\n睇得呢班D濕鳩youtuber UP埋D ON9野拍下打機生活片既都係D不問世事淨係識飲飲食食打機既小朋友<br />\n但你要明白 呢兩種youtuber既target group係完全唔同既<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上面燒山果班係全部都係資訊型既時事討論節目<br />\ntarget group係普遍年長少少既 同埋最重要係<ins>有心主動</ins>留意時事既人</span><br />\n下面果班你可以話係做緊類似娛樂節目型既youtuber KOL<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正正係下面呢一班youtuber<br />\n先target到平時唔留意時事既人<br />\ntarget到既人既層面先至係最廣</span></strong><br />\n可能佢地targer group平均都係10至18歲左右<br />\n但就係咁 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一班人係可塑性最高既人</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">將來變成藍定黃 就好睇佢地接收乜野資訊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>將來會唔會變成水魚中傳銷陷阱 <br />\n會唔會渴望做<strong><ins>台主</ins></strong>!(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 就好睇佢地接收乜野資訊</strong></span><br />\n所以都解釋左 點解政府會APPROACH呢一班KOL<br />\n同埋BUMP水養呢班KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家呢班人話自己係黃 食緊兩家茶禮<br />\n你估係真黃 定係滲透?<br />\n即使呢一刻食緊兩家茶禮既係背後都係真黃<br />\n但你儲左一班fans<br />\n過多幾年會唔會因為生計去變淺藍 影響呢班fans既價值觀?<br />\n你覺得過多幾年剷除異己之後班友會唔會現形?<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以呢單野同黃色經濟圈背後既理念基本上係相同</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講呢D係叫做捉鬼 係鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔好同我講唔好理屎家軍 有更重要既23條國歌法要理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有野係可以同步進行既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢幾日就係黃金時期去令更多人認識屎家軍 令更多人認識YOUTUBER KOL背後既生態<br />\n而家丟淡左既話 學片主話齋 暑假動漫節又係呢一班友既收成期了</span><br />\n<br />\n條片係提供哂証據同合理疑點<br />\n唔信既 下面呢度係原片 值得睇哂佢<br />\n再自己慢慢分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aQyYZ7YIVyY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaQyYZ7YIVyY&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=b0eab209\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aQyYZ7YIVyY</a>"},{"pid":"78417e2a766dee4591a818c4932328e8189118cd","tid":2023990,"uid":47144,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"呢單絕不是花生片"},{"pid":"c2c90fb56af701bede187ccbcf53d495f892cd61","tid":2023990,"uid":195540,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"趁依家個地步未去到挽回唔到既時候好做野<br />\n唔係話個個都藍 <br />\n但係班人咁撚蠢 比藍既利用左都唔知 <br />\n班真藍既味可以靠佢地護住<br />\n戈班自稱真黃既好諗清楚"},{"pid":"d54dbd1a8c9c2f111ab21011b2aad4322796821e","tid":2023990,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:59:31.000Z","msg":"截你老母圖"},{"pid":"d2af6e118e9188fe0e605afab342e1589fbd1aa4","tid":2023990,"uid":195540,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"帶頭用auman做擋箭牌戈個一係藍 一係就係死傻閪"},{"pid":"ca8bb7b85b83e61c3871b6922fe8eb82ff12579d","tid":2023990,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"d2af6e118e9188fe0e605afab342e1589fbd1aa4","tid":2023990,"uid":195540,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"帶頭用auman做擋箭牌戈個一係藍 一係就係死傻閪"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"邊個auman<br />\n咩黎?<br />\n我係咪miss左D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63461e56d1c5499b6d3d1e5bcdf888a385c9e0d0","tid":2023990,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82143e84d95bba42e8b1be39465271df5045b27","tid":2023990,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b14944b0862a969edda231d5d96390555ca037ac","tid":2023990,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d730afe2f29782b9fec726f7d9c80c2bcfd3f507","tid":2023990,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc3ce0e63a6c7f7bed41b97e0763401a4092d5ab","tid":2023990,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2c6fe8cbc29e8c04fe0fe053d9ba4ad3f395b79","tid":2023990,"uid":34107,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"睇曬成段片<br />\n主要問題係屎壟斷完個youtuber市場既話<br />\n到時灌輸極權思想會易入屋好多<br />\n當呢班youtuber習慣食開每年一億既電競資助<br />\n佢地仲敢講事實 講公道既說話？<br />\n大家可能要集思廣益睇下點樣抵抗佢地既壟斷"},{"pid":"602f90c5087334b194ca15edfd548e54c8587c66","tid":2023990,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:38:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79240ea595af19db4b5560384629583602257323","tid":2023990,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"4b6bd001337a21172226661936e06151342bc189","tid":2023990,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"fcafd0cb72df2e08e53d998c9c7c461ef1b1816e","tid":2023990,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:38:51.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"1c64a6707cbb11b361127b49168d7e1015e692ec","tid":2023990,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"92f6e759108357236dd795e0295cfc501187f9ad","tid":2023990,"uid":58010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:39:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5073d9487baed50b353d2b6f2dfa9668c68952f","tid":2023990,"uid":91321,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"垃圾兒登仔咁都畀人洗到腦<br />\n第時都冇出息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2436e7c31389279cb7ae82c34a463bb6a387433","tid":2023990,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ab10958c998c312165028c447b76422dfce4c5","tid":2023990,"uid":137818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score